  "description": "A wager is a stake placed on an uncertain outcome in [gambling](../index.md). The bettor risks something of value — typically money — against the possibility of receiving a larger return if their prediction proves correct. The terms of the wager specify what is staked, what outcomes qualify as a win, and what the payout will be, usually expressed as [odds](./odds.md).",
